== Pathology ==
Microscopical examination shows abundant thin-walled blood vessels with hypocellular and hypercellular areas. 

=== Immunohistochemistry ===
Almost all tumor cells have [[immunoreactivity]] for both desmin and vimentin. It also express [[estrogen receptor]]s and/or [[progesterone receptor]]s, but staining for [[cytokeratin]] is negative.<ref>{{Cite journal
